1
00:00:27,500 --> 00:00:29,820
=Soft-Hearted God=

2
00:00:29,820 --> 00:00:34,262
=Episode 23=
(My beloved, don't bear this pain alone.)

3
00:00:34,262 --> 00:00:35,399
(You still have me.)

4
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:45,480
The demon root isn't in your body.

5
00:00:45,840 --> 00:00:46,840
How could this be?

6
00:00:48,160 --> 00:00:49,680
I have suffered so greatly,

7
00:00:50,480 --> 00:00:51,600
yet failed to find it.

8
00:00:56,000 --> 00:00:56,520
Xi.

9
00:00:57,960 --> 00:00:58,440
Xi!

10
00:00:58,680 --> 00:00:59,320
Mother!

11
00:00:59,840 --> 00:01:00,320
Your Highness!

12
00:01:02,640 --> 00:01:03,520
Please take care of Xi.

13
00:01:16,040 --> 00:01:17,360
My wife...

14
00:01:18,240 --> 00:01:19,400
you cannot portray her well.

15
00:01:19,840 --> 00:01:21,080
The one I portray is,

16
00:01:21,760 --> 00:01:22,960
she who gouged out her heart,

17
00:01:23,520 --> 00:01:24,760
she who carved away her flesh,

18
00:01:25,200 --> 00:01:26,480
she who tore out her own eyes.

19
00:01:27,360 --> 00:01:28,800
Do I not resemble her?

20
00:01:33,800 --> 00:01:35,960
Where exactly is that wretched
demon root?

21
00:01:36,520 --> 00:01:37,760
I told you long ago,

22
00:01:38,360 --> 00:01:39,520
within the Three Realms,

23
00:01:39,840 --> 00:01:42,080
only the two of you can
find the demon root.

24
00:01:42,080 --> 00:01:43,640
Had you obeyed me back then

25
00:01:43,640 --> 00:01:44,800
and slain He Xi,

26
00:01:45,160 --> 00:01:46,840
none of these calamities
would have come to pass.

27
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:48,720
Even if I were given another chance,

28
00:01:49,640 --> 00:01:51,360
I would make the same choice.

29
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:53,000
As you wish.

30
00:01:53,280 --> 00:01:55,000
Watching you and your Xi

31
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:58,080
struggle endlessly within
the depths of love and hatred

32
00:01:58,720 --> 00:02:00,160
is, indeed, rather amusing.

33
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:02,560
Silence!

34
00:02:44,160 --> 00:02:45,360
I will not allow you

35
00:02:45,640 --> 00:02:47,320
to harm Father.

36
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,360
Demigod,

37
00:02:50,760 --> 00:02:51,920
you still remember me?

38
00:02:52,320 --> 00:02:53,200
Of course I do.

39
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:55,080
You forced me to buy your umbrella.

40
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:56,480
Spare me your feigned familiarity.

41
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:57,880
After hurting my father,

42
00:02:57,880 --> 00:02:58,960
you think you can walk away?

43
00:03:00,200 --> 00:03:00,960
Very well.

44
00:03:01,200 --> 00:03:02,360
Demigod, take a look.

45
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:04,040
Your father has recovered.

46
00:03:07,760 --> 00:03:08,680
Father.

47
00:03:09,760 --> 00:03:10,640
Are you all right?

48
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:59,320
She... her eyes glow with a crimson light.

49
00:03:59,600 --> 00:04:01,600
She's the exiled calamity princess!

50
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:03,920
Now that this plague runs rampant,

51
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:05,800
her portraits fill this entire house!

52
00:04:05,920 --> 00:04:07,080
This must be connected to her!

53
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:08,600
The palace rumors say

54
00:04:08,640 --> 00:04:09,920
whoever sees her crimson light

55
00:04:10,200 --> 00:04:11,080
is doomed to die.

56
00:04:23,960 --> 00:04:25,360
If anyone dares lay a hand on her again,

57
00:04:26,200 --> 00:04:27,400
the next thing shattered

58
00:04:28,400 --> 00:04:30,200
will be your heads.

59
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:43,800
Human nature remains unchanged.

60
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:53,640
Zhao!

61
00:04:58,800 --> 00:04:59,560
He's a deity!

62
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:00,080
Zhao.

63
00:05:00,200 --> 00:05:01,520
I heard eating a deity's flesh and blood

64
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:03,120
can cure our illness!

65
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:15,320
It's a last-ditch effort.

66
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:16,800
I'll try it on behalf of everyone!

67
00:05:29,080 --> 00:05:29,440
Zhao!

68
00:05:29,440 --> 00:05:30,000
Father!

69
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:31,640
Zhao.

70
00:05:33,120 --> 00:05:33,560
Zhao!

71
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:34,760
Assault!

72
00:05:36,320 --> 00:05:37,240
Assault

73
00:05:38,320 --> 00:05:39,760
He's attacking the sick!

74
00:05:40,440 --> 00:05:41,240
He's attacking the sick!

75
00:05:42,440 --> 00:05:43,360
He's attacking the sick!

76
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:44,520
So it's true.

77
00:05:46,440 --> 00:05:47,240
It does not seem so.

78
00:05:51,320 --> 00:05:52,680
You are from the palace, aren't you?

79
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:56,560
Ordinary citizens
wouldn't know who I am.

80
00:05:57,880 --> 00:05:58,800
They're from the palace?

81
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:14,560
Your Highness, he's the shadow
guard of Helian Shu.

82
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:17,880
I was just about
to settle accounts with him,

83
00:06:18,760 --> 00:06:21,120
yet he has delivered himself
to me uninvited.

84
00:06:22,440 --> 00:06:23,240
Take him away.

85
00:06:23,520 --> 00:06:25,080
Interrogate him and find Helian Shu.

86
00:06:25,880 --> 00:06:27,240
Guards, take him into custody!

87
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:27,880
Yes!

88
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:32,200
Your Highness, please save us!

89
00:06:32,440 --> 00:06:35,080
Your Highness, we only wish to live!

90
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:37,560
Your Highness!

91
00:06:37,880 --> 00:06:38,360
Your Highness,

92
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:39,520
please help us!

93
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:46,560
Your Highness!

94
00:06:46,880 --> 00:06:47,440
Your Highness,

95
00:06:47,440 --> 00:06:48,520
please help us!

96
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:50,200
Help us!

97
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:56,240
Your Highness, please save us!

98
00:06:59,200 --> 00:07:01,320
Have mercy on us, Your Highness!

99
00:07:02,080 --> 00:07:03,240
Your Highness!

100
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:05,240
(Mother,)

101
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:08,440
(what should Xihe do?)

102
00:07:10,080 --> 00:07:11,000
(Is the State of Ning)

103
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:14,640
(to be destroyed by my own hands?)

104
00:07:26,880 --> 00:07:27,880
Mother,

105
00:07:28,440 --> 00:07:29,880
you treat patients by day

106
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:31,120
and study by night.

107
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:33,120
You have not rested for three days.

108
00:07:35,880 --> 00:07:37,000
Has it truly been that long?

109
00:07:37,320 --> 00:07:38,240
Yes.

110
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:40,760
It pains me to see you like this.

111
00:07:41,320 --> 00:07:42,880
Please, rest tonight.

112
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:45,200
I beg you.

113
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:51,560
If I can find a solution sooner,

114
00:07:52,320 --> 00:07:55,560
I can end their suffering sooner.

115
00:07:57,440 --> 00:07:58,360
Mother,

116
00:07:58,640 --> 00:08:00,050
you aren't a deity.

117
00:08:00,440 --> 00:08:01,880
You are mortal.

118
00:08:03,750 --> 00:08:04,870
Be good now.

119
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:07,320
It's true, I'm mortal,

120
00:08:07,920 --> 00:08:09,120
but I'm also a physician

121
00:08:10,320 --> 00:08:11,920
and the princess of Ning State.

122
00:08:13,080 --> 00:08:14,440
Go and check on your father first,

123
00:08:14,760 --> 00:08:15,440
all right?

124
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:22,640
Father.

125
00:08:27,320 --> 00:08:28,360
Why have you gotten up?

126
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:32,120
I have nearly recovered.

127
00:08:33,760 --> 00:08:34,320
Look.

128
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:36,120
Perhaps it's because

129
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:37,560
I did not take their lives,

130
00:08:37,800 --> 00:08:38,760
the backlash is minimal.

131
00:08:38,880 --> 00:08:39,760
Father,

132
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:42,240
please persuade Mother.

133
00:08:42,240 --> 00:08:43,000
If this continues,

134
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,520
her body will give out.

135
00:08:46,880 --> 00:08:47,760
Go outside for now.

136
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:49,800
Your mother and I need to speak.

137
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:00,120
Why not rest first

138
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:02,800
and wait until later, when we...

139
00:09:03,760 --> 00:09:04,560
Later?

140
00:09:05,520 --> 00:09:07,200
How many "laters"
are there in this world?

141
00:09:07,440 --> 00:09:08,520
In the past, I failed

142
00:09:08,760 --> 00:09:10,520
and the entire village became flower thralls.

143
00:09:11,520 --> 00:09:12,880
If I fail this time,

144
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:15,720
all the people of Ning State will die!

145
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:17,720
How can you ask me to wait for "later"?

146
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:20,000
Why is it that even you...

147
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:22,840
cannot understand me?

148
00:09:41,520 --> 00:09:42,280
I'm sorry.

149
00:10:11,760 --> 00:10:12,760
Right now,

150
00:10:15,880 --> 00:10:17,160
you must get proper rest.

151
00:10:18,480 --> 00:10:19,600
When you awaken,

152
00:10:20,880 --> 00:10:22,240
everything will be better.

153
00:10:23,520 --> 00:10:24,280
(Xi...)

154
00:10:25,120 --> 00:10:26,640
(Bone worm failed
to find the demon root,)

155
00:10:27,520 --> 00:10:29,160
(it has sealed the demon heart.)

156
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:31,520
(She can no longer
possess another body.)

157
00:10:32,760 --> 00:10:34,240
(As long as all the patients are cured,)

158
00:10:35,480 --> 00:10:37,240
(your life will be safe
and without worry.)

159
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:22,280
(Baobao.)

160
00:11:24,240 --> 00:11:24,760
That's good.

161
00:11:26,160 --> 00:11:27,480
Mother has finally fallen asleep.

162
00:11:30,880 --> 00:11:32,760
What is it, Father?

163
00:11:32,760 --> 00:11:33,520
Nothing.

164
00:11:34,640 --> 00:11:35,400
Baobao,

165
00:11:36,880 --> 00:11:38,880
in a few days, it will be the full moon.

166
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:40,920
I'll transfer my divine power to you,

167
00:11:41,760 --> 00:11:43,280
in case my own powers
are completely depleted

168
00:11:44,360 --> 00:11:45,280
and flower slaves attack.

169
00:11:58,640 --> 00:12:01,520
Help your mother back to bed.

170
00:12:03,880 --> 00:12:05,400
Do not leave her side for even a moment.

171
00:12:06,480 --> 00:12:07,000
All right.

172
00:12:33,587 --> 00:12:35,475
(Martial Hall)

173
00:12:38,280 --> 00:12:39,640
Immortal, are you...

174
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:42,040
I'm unharmed.

175
00:12:44,640 --> 00:12:47,000
Tonight, I will cast a spell

176
00:12:47,360 --> 00:12:49,160
to cure all those afflicted
with Verdant Decay.

177
00:12:49,920 --> 00:12:50,760
At that time,

178
00:12:51,920 --> 00:12:54,160
I will endure tens of thousands
of lightning punishments

179
00:12:56,280 --> 00:12:58,280
until I am reduced to ashes.

180
00:12:59,760 --> 00:13:01,000
Baobao has freed herself

181
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:02,640
from dependence on my divine power.

182
00:13:03,800 --> 00:13:04,400
But...

183
00:13:04,680 --> 00:13:06,160
I'm not discussing this with you.

184
00:13:06,400 --> 00:13:07,520
There are three matters

185
00:13:08,640 --> 00:13:10,160
you must accomplish.

186
00:13:10,920 --> 00:13:11,680
First,

187
00:13:12,240 --> 00:13:14,280
hunt down all fugitive flower slaves.

188
00:13:15,520 --> 00:13:17,040
You must ensure

189
00:13:17,560 --> 00:13:20,120
they never see the light of day again.

190
00:13:20,760 --> 00:13:21,520
Second,

191
00:13:22,640 --> 00:13:24,880
take good care of Xi and Baobao.

192
00:13:26,640 --> 00:13:29,520
Do not let them suffer
even the slightest harm.

193
00:13:31,560 --> 00:13:32,400
Third.

194
00:13:33,850 --> 00:13:36,112
(Martial Hall)

195
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:36,480
There are 28,000 patients in Ning State.

196
00:14:36,480 --> 00:14:39,360
You shall endure 28,000 bolts
of heavenly lightning.

197
00:14:39,360 --> 00:14:41,480
How interesting... how very interesting.

198
00:14:51,880 --> 00:14:53,360
Stop at once!

199
00:14:53,360 --> 00:14:57,000
If you continue,
you'll be reduced to ashes!

200
00:15:09,400 --> 00:15:10,120
It's gone.

201
00:15:10,400 --> 00:15:11,200
Master,

202
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:12,720
all the flower pollen we collected

203
00:15:12,720 --> 00:15:13,960
has completely vanished!

204
00:15:14,600 --> 00:15:16,240
We're cured!

205
00:15:16,240 --> 00:15:17,840
We no longer have to suffer!

206
00:15:29,360 --> 00:15:30,120
An immortal is outside,

207
00:15:30,120 --> 00:15:31,080
a miracle has appeared!

208
00:15:31,080 --> 00:15:31,880
Let's go out and see!

209
00:15:31,880 --> 00:15:32,760
Yes, quickly!

210
00:15:32,760 --> 00:15:33,640
Go and take a look!

211
00:15:33,680 --> 00:15:34,200
Come on!

212
00:15:39,120 --> 00:15:40,480
Thank you, Immortal!

213
00:15:40,480 --> 00:15:41,960
May the Immortal bless us!

214
00:16:03,800 --> 00:16:05,510
♪Even if reluctant, what can be done♪

215
00:16:05,510 --> 00:16:08,090
♪Chasing something always out of reach♪

216
00:16:08,360 --> 00:16:11,100
♪So I'm afraid of goodbye♪

217
00:16:11,100 --> 00:16:12,730
♪Living the same day
over and over again♪

218
00:16:12,730 --> 00:16:18,010
(Perhaps, if I reincarnate,)

219
00:16:18,380 --> 00:16:19,980
(I can rid myself of this demon heart.)

220
00:16:19,980 --> 00:16:22,550
(I will definitely
come back to find you.)

221
00:16:22,740 --> 00:16:25,450
(You must wait for me.)

222
00:16:25,590 --> 00:16:28,190
♪If in a dream♪

223
00:16:28,190 --> 00:16:32,680
♪I can hear your voice♪

224
00:16:32,980 --> 00:16:34,740
♪Then let it be our meeting♪

225
00:16:34,740 --> 00:16:37,070
♪Let it be us♪

226
00:16:37,610 --> 00:16:40,030
♪drawing endlessly close♪

227
00:16:40,330 --> 00:16:41,980
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

228
00:16:41,980 --> 00:16:47,410
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

229
00:16:47,640 --> 00:16:49,180
♪I can't even hold you properly♪

230
00:16:49,180 --> 00:16:51,930
♪Not even in time♪

231
00:16:51,930 --> 00:16:54,900
♪to tell you how I feel♪

232
00:16:54,900 --> 00:16:57,450
♪If the rain won't stop♪

233
00:16:57,450 --> 00:17:01,780
♪If the wind won't fade,
if time stands still♪

234
00:17:02,090 --> 00:17:04,540
♪Let love go on♪

235
00:17:04,700 --> 00:17:11,490
♪Until forever♪
